Package com.cloudera.cdk.data.dao

Interface Summary
Dao<K,E> Interface for HBase Common DAOs.
EntityBatch<K,E>  
EntityScanner<K,E> A Scanner interface that represents an Iterable that allows us to iterate over entities in an HBase table, returning them as KeyEntity instances.
SchemaManager Interface for managing schemas with a meta store.
 

Class Summary
Constants HBase Common Library Constants
EntitySchema An EntitySchema is the parsed schema that contains the properties of an HBase Common entity schema.
EntitySchema.FieldMapping A field mapping represents a type that specifies how a schema field maps to a column in HBase.
KeyEntity<K,E> A class that encapsulates a Key and an Entity which is returned from the EntityMapper mapToEntity function.
KeySchema The KeySchema type.
PartialKey<K> A partial key, which can be used to create table scanners that start from the bytes that make up only part of the key.
PartialKey.Builder<K> Builder for the PartialKey
PartialKey.KeyPartNameValue A class that encapsulates a Key part.
 

Enum Summary
MappingType The supported Mapping Types, which control how an entity field maps to columns in an HBase table.
 

Exception Summary
ConcurrentSchemaModificationException An exception that indicates a managed schema modification collided with another client trying to modify that same managed schema.
HBaseClientException Wraps IOExceptions exceptions thrown by the HBase Client API.
HBaseCommonException The base Exception type for HBase Common.
IncompatibleSchemaException  
KeyBuildException Exception that is thrown when the construction of a Key fails with an error.
SchemaNotFoundException  
SchemaValidationException  
SerializationException
